    "ts": "1708633333.287589",
    "client_msg_id": "bd0fd27d-41fa-4c97-83dc-5c69df9c2072",
    "text": "Yeah I came here to say Enso.\n\nAlso wanted to note: I assume you meant “statically”, and it got autocorrected to “statistically”. But I really, really like the idea of a statistically-typed language! Maybe you could declare variables like `(30% int, 70% string) myVar`.",
